    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ol>
<li><p><strong>安装samba</strong></p>
<pre><code>sudo apt-get install samba system-config-samba samba-client samba-common 
</code></pre></li>
<li><p><strong>打开/etc/samba/smb.con，添加如下内容</strong></p>
<pre><code>[aliyun]
path = /root
valid users = root
writeable = yes
printable = no
create mask = 0777
directory mask = 0777
</code></pre></li>
<li><p><strong>重启samba服务</strong></p>
<pre><code>service sambd restart
</code></pre></li>
</ol>
]]></content>
